Enhancement: Add SSE events for locking, renaming, deleting, and restoring

We've added Server-Sent Events (SSE) for locking, renaming, deleting, and restoring actions.
This enhancements ensures that these actions are instantly propagated to other browsers and devices where the user is logged in.
Now, users can experience real-time updates across all their devices.

